## Structural Conflict with Existing Proofs Page

**Current state:** `content/proofs/` has no `_index.md`. It contains only `bishop-prediction-bp073.md` and an empty `charts_bp058/` directory. There is no existing narrative page to replace at that URL.

**Recommendation:** Create `content/proofs/_index.md` with the new draft. The prediction file (`bishop-prediction-bp073.md`) stays as a sub-page and is linked from the Tier 3 section.

**URL:** `/proofs/` (already the canonical path; no redirect needed)

**Frontmatter note:** The draft uses `slug: "proofs"` which is redundant with the directory name but harmless. Hugo will serve at `/proofs/` either way.

**Layout:** No dedicated `layouts/proofs/` exists. Hugo will use the default section template. If the site has a content-class CSS system (the `class` frontmatter field suggests it does), the `empirical-proofs` class may need a corresponding style rule. Check with Knight or look at how other class values render.

